#This is a README file dealing with the actual structure of the 
#Course Project directory.
#Created by D.Dakhno
#######################################################################

Due to version incompatibility of R Markdown v2 the files commited (.Rmd, .md., .html) had to be processed and generated in a way, different from that proposed in assignment (so, not with knit2html(), but either within of RStudio or with rmarkdown::render(..., clear = FALSE)).

RStudio(Version 0.99.491) in combination with R (version 3.2.3) leaves 
no intermediate .md-files after generating the html-version.

To meet the requirements of the assignment I included both versions of each generated file. Here the way to distinguisch them:
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
File                    |       Origin
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
PA1_template.Rmd        |       Written in RStudio  
PA1_template.html       |       Generated through RStudio
PA1_template.knit.html  |       Generated through rmarkdown::render()
PA1_template.knit.md    |       Generated through rmarkdown::render()
PA1_template.utf8.md    |       Generated through rmarkdown::render()
PA1_template_files      |       Generated through rmarkdown::render()
README                  |       This file
README.html             |       Generated through RStudio from original README.md               |       Original README.md
-----------------------------------------------------------------------                     
                                